{"tid":104500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"碩士博士月薪得1萬　大學生值何價？","createTime":"2017-02-02T07:09:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T11:33:37.000Z","uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a807e0decb1e133d994df052937d82ee4199a139","tid":104500,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T07:09:42.000Z","msg":"勞工處日前推出高等學歷就業資訊網上平台，職位空缺均最低要求學士學歷，薪酬低見7,000元起、高見9萬元，亦有公司開極低價月薪1萬元，招聘碩士或博士學歷的學校課程編寫員。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1575000/1576859/work_thumb_20161229_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1575000%2F1576859%2Fwork_thumb_20161229_1024.jpg&h=e68fd3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTOPick記者翻查平台上的職位空缺，涵蓋多個行業如金融、中醫、科技、教育、進出口等。有醫療集團招聘3年年資的註冊中醫師，底薪連佣金每月7,000元起至1.6萬元；亦有公關公司以9,800元至1萬元聘請公關主任，惟根據TOPick早前報道，初入行的公關月入一般介乎1.1萬至1.3萬，視乎公司規模及類型。<br />\n<br />\n有教育機構聘請合約STEM課程編寫員，合約期約8個半月，5天工作，朝9晚6，要求申請者需有碩士或博士學位，但僅開價月薪1萬元，即時薪約56元。<br />\n<img src=\"http://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1575000/1576859/stem_course_master_1024.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1575000%2F1576859%2Fstem_course_master_1024.JPG&h=93d5780e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n安俊人力資源顧問董事總經理周綺萍直指，即使是學士畢業生，起薪點起碼1萬元，如要聘請碩士生此價遠低於市場水平。<br />\n<br />\n不過她相信，即使薪水不合理地低，仍有來港讀碩士或博士課程的內地生願意應徵，因內地生在香港搵工不易，他們想得到在港工作的經驗，「寫靚份CV，增加個人價值」，不介意薪水較低。"},{"pid":"247fba8b7846deb5ae785a2bb40f24fc15bac729","tid":104500,"uid":48442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T07:12:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5ca7b5383cc29bdbc8d7675e677812fead6a11f","tid":104500,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T07:15:18.000Z","msg":"IT狗差唔多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97c0ceeda857be7e2681d7982ddb17a0708a637","tid":104500,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T07:17:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>IT狗差唔多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n@老貓_二世"},{"pid":"e1b29d78d244ade3277bf3fc0312c7b22cc0beb5","tid":104500,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T07:54:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac250c6103b4bee4caed3ce4eeaee6b2c45938c","tid":104500,"uid":63721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:03:30.000Z","msg":"學歷高就月薪高?<br />\n錯哂啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add1b6f62cc6e88260d62bd70d8732e7546ac2a4","tid":104500,"uid":20531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:16:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學歷高就月薪高?<br />\n錯哂啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n社會已經變左，<br />\n需要既唔再係學歷，而係專業技能"},{"pid":"2901505a1e9008ad76e687f3a66411f6577f6933","tid":104500,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:20:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"760d6b2f84b2823519a5bde3d918ec63e4510d33","tid":104500,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:27:06.000Z","msg":"bettrer than IT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28dcf7e0a6fd354e8646ef457883c9c972c085b0","tid":104500,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:32:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">不過她相信，即使薪水不合理地低，仍有來港讀碩士或博士課程的內地生願意應徵，因內地生在香港搵工不易，他們想得到在港工作的經驗，「寫靚份CV，增加個人價值」，不介意薪水較低。</span><br />\n<br />\n即係話班大陸人會頂爛市，你班香港人食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0703446ccbe43bdd5182948cd79f8cd6fabf7052","tid":104500,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:35:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1480000/1481730/taikoo_thumb_20160812_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1480000%2F1481730%2Ftaikoo_thumb_20160812_1024.jpg&h=864dee02&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0cce8ecb7f6bbfb06ad94fe0306c7b93874dc997","tid":104500,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:40:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢d工係比班大陸喱來講讀完master後，要份到工做夠7年就變永久居民<br />\n如果佢地搵唔到工，就要番大陸</blockquote><br />\n所以免費都做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db34ed5309e04f1d621a24c8bfe7866376c269c6","tid":104500,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:41:42.000Z","msg":"因內地生在香港搵工不易?我唔信<br />\n<br />\n連登仔話成個金融界都支那人喎，明顯係自己讀錯科啦"},{"pid":"f7837bcf491d60081295a663ad291752ed1537cd","tid":104500,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:44:24.000Z","msg":"資深海事處小輪船員督導員在2014至2015年間謊報上班時間，企圖欺詐及誘使海事處職員批核3129元逾時工作補貼。督導員承認一項欺詐罪，代表律師指他只是出於「公務員習性」才填寫虛假出勤記錄，並非有意欺詐<br />\n<br />\n案情指，被告張偉星（47歲）作為小輪船員督導員，工作時間為上午8時至下午5時，因工作需要他須額外延長上班時間，獲超時工作補貼。但被告自2014年11月至2015年12月間，曾11次遲到早退，仍遞交虛假的值勤記錄及超時工作津貼申請表，並虛假地向海事處職員表示有關資料準確。<br />\n<br />\n被告中三學歷，在海事處工作26年，現負責安排船隻維修，須24小時候命救船，月入3.5萬元，上月20日已被停職，被告家中有一名患子宮頸癌的母親，無妻無子女。辯方求情指，被告並非有意欺騙「補水」，只是出於公務員習性，機械式呈交出勤記錄和申領補貼文件，辯方又呈上16封求情信，希望裁判官輕判。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">被告中三學歷，月入3.5萬元</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中三廢老反而有35000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82df9084c51880cb2fa50460891b42352fe29ae0","tid":104500,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T09:28:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa2e38635d4b9bd4397fec8b8ffda3629cbf77cb","tid":104500,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T09:30:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/d3501404780492z13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fd3501404780492z13.jpg&h=ec51041c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n一般紀律人員(員佐級)薪級表第 4 點(每月 19,780 元)至一般紀律人員(員佐級)薪級表第14 點(每月 27,380 元)。"},{"pid":"8dab3bfec5ee6dbfc010cd91aa3a5890db66a167","tid":104500,"uid":38041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T09:31:25.000Z","msg":"未load到圖 係咪都講咗晴報先實冇死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573019abba0709c8d96ba1bb0e6759dd445abaa3","tid":104500,"uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T09:34:12.000Z","msg":"讀完ive出黎都1.2m起表啦，仲讀博士黎托咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a76d418583b8603161b4f63ff348b90aeb89a9","tid":104500,"uid":57700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T09:34:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"58608d0a91e33761293d3bd017934dbe37365d14","tid":104500,"uid":32676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T09:36:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀完ive出黎都1.2m起表啦，仲讀博士黎托咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nIVE league<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nFresh grad百二萬一個月"},{"pid":"e0d329480aee30a807bd249c292e90abc35b97f9","tid":104500,"uid":33783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T09:37:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>學歷高就月薪高?<br />\n錯哂啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n社會已經變左，<br />\n需要既唔再係學歷，而係專業技能</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIT唔撚專業咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0fca4edadd41b3402d403bf2310a151c74de62f","tid":104500,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T09:40:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"647166c4095fc7750243cb98d03be8036a6cf5a5","tid":104500,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:10:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀完大學入唔到公帽員，香港只有金融雞sales 狗兩條上位途徑，呢D呃騙行業反而頭腦越簡單越易洗腦，讀得書多道德越高反而多制抓，工種單一，讀書咁多科得無所有，香港係炒賣者天地，仆街誠得小三學歷，最緊要識擦鞋</blockquote><br />\n巴打所言極是，香港地真係仆街先易上位"},{"pid":"676766c9e9338c489d142a4a4a64cada0dc035a0","tid":104500,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T11:40:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f55dd58a8fe80dcd85ba9b3054d9c01b5d7f9b65","tid":104500,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T11:54:08.000Z","msg":"碩士博士，通街都係，一文不值"}]}